00:42:39.640 --> 00:42:41.520
[Guest]: So what can they do with their organization?

00:42:41.520 --> 00:42:45.280
[Guest]: And in states which are bipolar states, we are speaking at an interesting moment because

00:42:45.280 --> 00:42:50.960
[Guest]: the next six elections, big elections in India, Gujarat, Himachal, Karnataka, MP, Chhattisgarh,

00:42:50.960 --> 00:42:55.520
