00:42:55.520 --> 00:43:00.560
[Guest]: So in bipolar states, how does Congress manage to beat the BJP, and in states where Congress

00:43:00.560 --> 00:43:04.220
[Guest]: is weak, does it stitch up a grand alliance of anti-BJP forces?

00:43:04.220 --> 00:43:08.080
[Guest]: So the state of the opposition and what that will look like at the end of 2018, early 2019

00:43:08.080 --> 00:43:10.480
[Guest]: will also be an important variable.

00:43:10.480 --> 00:43:14.640
[Guest]: Every election is open, 2019 election is not a done deal.

00:43:14.640 --> 00:43:19.520
